item.title: CVE-2023-44298|2023-12-05T15:57:54.738Z -- dell -- poweredge%20bios
item.description: Dell PowerEdge platforms 16G Intel E5 BIOS and Dell Precision BIOS, version 1.4.4, contain active debug code security vulnerability. An unauthenticated physical attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to information tampering, code execution, denial of service.
